      "title": "An electric tricycle is launched",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sri Lanka's leading three-wheeler supplier, David Peiris Motor Company, launched an electric three-wheeler today (16).",
        "The American Agency for International Development and David Peirce Motor Company signed the Memorandum of Understanding for this project.",
        "A group of people including the American Ambassador to Sri Lanka and the Minister of Power and Energy Mr. Kanchana Wijesekera participated in this event."
      ],
